column16: Stonecutter #29 - Possibly the devil? Born in 1886. Contact Waylon Smithers if needing to get in touch with Burns.
An alien - always trying to eat people - exercise caution around
Sold the town a terrible unsafe monorail. Sold our money while trying to steal our hearts...   MONORAIL!
Has a strong obsession with trying to kill Bart Simpson for some reason...
